Package: gcfboardr
Type: Package
Title: A text dataset harvested from Green Climate Fund Board documents
Version: 0.1.0
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: 
    dplyr
Suggests:
    tidytext,
    ggplot2,
    purrr,
    pdftools,
    readr,
    testthat
Authors@R: person("Liam", "O'Dea", email = "liam.j.odea@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A dataset ready for text analysis, mined from 500+ pdf documents 
    published by The Green Climate Fund (GCF). Data covers GCF board meetings from 
    2012 to 2017. See The Green Climate Fund website for the original documents used 
    to build the dataset.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
